msgctxt "UITextData/Overall_Graphics_Description"
msgid ""
"A set of graphics settings customized in an attempt to give you the most "
"control possible over how our game is rendered and how you'd like to balance "
"quality and performance while still being understandable if you don't know a "
"ton about graphics and GPUs.\n"
"\n"
"Change a setting to see an overview and description of what it does!\n"
"\n"
"While we do encourage you to dive into these settings, we have spent quite a "
"bit of time configuring tailored presets for as many GPUs as we have been "
"able to get our hands on, including your...\n"
"\n"
"*drumroll*"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "UITextData/Overall_Immersion_Description"
msgid ""
"A set of immersion related settings to help personalize your experience.\n"
"\n"
"Change a setting to see an overview and description of what it does!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "UITextData/GPreset_Description"
msgid ""
"A set of overall graphics presets that scale all quality and detail "
"settings.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Medium</>:  The most performance-focused preset. Still very detailed "
"and good looking.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>High</>:  The default quality setting and the preset all our gameplay "
"and “renders” have been recorded on. No need to go higher than this.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Unreasonable</>:  You don’t need this.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>Tailored</>:  A preset specifically designed for your PC (GPU & CPU) "
"to target a smooth 60fps."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "UITextData/Overall_General_Description"
msgid ""
"A set of the most common settings players like to adjust.\n"
"\n"
"If you’d like something added here, reach out and we’ll get it in.\n"
"\n"
"Change a setting to see an overview and explanation of what it does!"
msgstr ""

