msgctxt "UITextData/Upscaler_Description"
msgid ""
"Improves performance by rendering at a lower resolution and scaling the "
"image back up. Quality depends on your GPU and the mode you choose.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>None</>:  No upscaling. Sharpest image but the heaviest on "
"performance.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>DLSS</>:  NVIDIA-only. Delivers strong performance boosts with very "
"sharp AI-assisted reconstruction.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>FSR</>:  Works on almost any GPU. Good performance and decent "
"sharpness, though not as clean as DLSS.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>XeSS</>:  Best on Intel GPUs but works on others. Similar to DLSS-"
"style upscaling, with quality varying by hardware."
msgstr ""

