msgctxt "UITextData/Antialiasing_Description"
msgid ""
"Reduces jagged edges and shimmering. Higher options look smoother but may "
"soften the image or use more GPU power.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>None</>:  No smoothing. Sharp but very jagged, especially in motion.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>FXAA</>:  Fast and cheap. Smooths edges lightly but can blur small "
"details.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>TAA</>:  Stable, good overall quality. Softens the image a bit but "
"removes most shimmer.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>TSR</>:  Best quality. Sharper than TAA and works beautifully paired "
"with upscaling, but uses more GPU."
msgstr ""

