msgctxt "UITextData/Vsync_Description"
msgid ""
"Synchronizes the game’s frame rate with your monitor to prevent screen "
"tearing. Can slightly increase input latency.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>OFF</>:  No syncing. Faster input response, but tearing may appear "
"during fast movement.\n"
"\n"
"<Bold>ON</>:  Smooths out tearing by matching frames to your display’s "
"refresh rate, at the cost of a bit more latency."
msgstr ""

